Package org.junit.platform.engine

Interface DiscoverySelector

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClasspathResourceSelector, ClasspathRootSelector, ClassSelector, DirectorySelector, FileSelector, MethodSelector, PackageSelector, UniqueIdSelector, UriSelector

    @API(status=STABLE,
     since="1.0")
public interface DiscoverySelector
    A selector defines what a TestEngine can use to discover tests — for example, the name of a Java class, the path to a file or directory, etc.
    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    EngineDiscoveryRequest
